        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sweet potato is fork-tender, add the <strong>brown rice </strong>and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>crème fraîche</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) to the pan and give everything a good mix up until fully combined</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>sweet potato & green bean rice</strong></p>",
